<bibRefCitation author="Halliday, R. B. &amp; Norton, R. A." box="[960,1241,1050,1077]" pageId="12" pageNumber="513" pagination="34 - 42" refId="ref21440" refString="Halliday, R. B. &amp; Norton, R. A. (2019) Case 3785 - Proposal to remove the homonymy of Cepheidae Berlese, 1896 (Acariformes) with Cepheidae Agassiz, 1862 (Cnidaria), by emending the former to Cepheusidae. Bulletin of Zoological Nomenclature, 76, 34 - 42. https: // doi. org / 10.21805 / bzn. v 76. a 010" type="journal article" year="2019">Halliday &amp; Norton 2019</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
